03/01/2003
ZAGREB, Croatia -- President Stipe Mesic met new Army Chief-of-Staff Lt Gen Josip Lucic on Thursday (2 January). Lucic took over from Gen Petar Stipetic on Tuesday, in keeping with efforts to reform the army by promoting younger professionals to higher levels in the chain of command. The cabinet is expected to approve Lucic's appointment Friday. (HINA - 02/01/03)
